title: The Main Gnomish Ethnicity Used To Enslave The Main Human Population
content: The smallest species currently known to Helsi are the Gnomes. These tiny creatures are the heart of technological innovation and advancement. Their wittiness and humour makes it impossible to hate them. However, they do have a dark past with the humans, especially considering that they used to enslave them. The @[The Barbaric Uprise](militaryConflict:ae463ee0-414a-4095-ba48-5dc3eda8dc4d) brought an end to that era for the Gnomes and they have been collaborative ever since.
